{"node_id": "56de8254d3555ae0bbb15a58b0fb17c0", "title": "Combining like terms with rational coefficients", "description": "Practice combining like terms for expressions that have rational coefficients. This requires adding and subtracting fractions.", "topic_path": ["Khan Academy (English - US curriculum)", "Math by grade", "High school", "Get ready for Algebra 1", "Get ready for equations & inequalities", "Combining like terms", "Combining like terms with rational coefficients"], "assessment_items": [{"item_id": "5b5580681d0e5a48979c85dda819e384", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  ${-\\dfrac{4}{7}p+(-\\dfrac27p)+\\dfrac17}$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $p$ terms.\n\n", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{-\\dfrac{4}{7}}p+(\\blue{-\\dfrac27}p)+\\dfrac17}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac{4}{7}}+\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac27}\\right)\\right)\\cdot p+\\dfrac17$\n\n$=\\left({-\\dfrac{6}{7}}\\right)\\cdot p+\\dfrac17$\n\n$={-\\dfrac{6}{7}}\\ p+\\dfrac17$", "The simplified expression is ${-\\dfrac{6}{7}}\\ p+\\dfrac17$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-\\frac{6}{7}p+\\frac{1}{7}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-\\frac{6}{7}p+\\frac{1}{7}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "e24f3d52c60a531981ac6e32072c7efe", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  ${\\dfrac{2}{5}m-\\dfrac45-\\dfrac35m}$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $m$ terms.\n\n", "\n$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{\\dfrac{2}{5}}m-\\dfrac45-\\blue{\\dfrac35}m}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{\\dfrac{2}{5}}-\\blue{\\dfrac35}\\right)\\cdot m-\\dfrac45$\n\n$=\\left({-\\dfrac{1}{5}}\\right)\\cdot m-\\dfrac45$\n\n$=-\\dfrac15m-\\dfrac45$", "The simplified expression is ${-\\dfrac{1}{5}m-\\dfrac45}\\ $"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-\\frac{1}{5}m-\\frac{4}{5}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-\\frac{1}{5}m-\\frac{4}{5}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "e63177c865025fc5adda071a70e21095", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n${-\\dfrac{2}{3}a+\\dfrac56a-\\dfrac16}$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $a$ terms.\n\n", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}a+\\blue{\\dfrac56}a-\\dfrac16}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}+\\blue{\\dfrac56}\\right)\\cdot a-\\dfrac16$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n${=}\\left({-\\dfrac{4}{6}}+{\\dfrac56}\\right)\\cdot a-\\dfrac16$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{1}{6}}\\right)\\cdot a-\\dfrac16$ \n\n$=\\dfrac{1}{6}a-\\dfrac16$", "The simplified expression is $\\dfrac{1}{6}a-\\dfrac16$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["\\frac{1}{6}a-\\frac{1}{6}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "\\frac{1}{6}a-\\frac{1}{6}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "891aeb5315045940b93f881a691e763a", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to simplify the expression: **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  ${\\dfrac{2}{5}k-\\dfrac35+\\dfrac{1}{10}k}$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $k$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{\\dfrac{2}{5}}k-\\dfrac35+\\blue{\\dfrac{1}{10}}k}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{\\dfrac{2}{5}}+\\blue{\\dfrac{1}{10}}\\right)\\cdot k-\\dfrac35$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{4}{10}}+{\\dfrac{1}{10}}\\right)\\cdot k-\\dfrac35$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{5}{10}}\\right)\\cdot k-\\dfrac35$\n\n$=\\left({{\\dfrac{1}{2}}}\\right)\\cdot k-\\dfrac35$ [[☃ explanation 3]]\n\n$=\\dfrac12k-\\dfrac35$", "The simplified expression is $\\dfrac12k-\\dfrac35$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["\\frac{1}{2}k-\\frac{3}{5}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": "0", "simplify": true, "value": "\\frac{1}{2}k-\\frac{3}{5}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "36fb167c5b55500db6f45c1d6c949888", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n$\\dfrac{9}{8}m+\\dfrac{9}{10}-2m-\\dfrac35$  \n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blueE{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $m$ terms, and combine the $\\maroonE{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blueE{\\dfrac{9}{8}}m+\\maroonE{\\dfrac{9}{10}}\\blueE{-2}m-\\maroonE{\\dfrac35}}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blueE{\\dfrac{9}{8}}-\\blueE{2}\\right)\\cdot m+\\maroonE{\\dfrac{9}{10}}-\\maroonE{\\dfrac35}$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{9}{8}}-{\\dfrac{16}{8}}\\right)\\cdot m+\\dfrac{9}{10}-\\dfrac{6}{10}$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n$=\\left({-\\dfrac{7}{8}}\\right)\\cdot m+\\dfrac{3}{10}$\n\n$=-\\dfrac78m+\\dfrac{3}{10}$", "The simplified expression is $-\\dfrac{7}{8}m+\\dfrac{3}{10}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-\\frac{7}{8}m+\\frac{3}{10}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-\\frac{7}{8}m+\\frac{3}{10}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "fb4c61dfd710567295a78a32716a9605", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  $-\\dfrac65-\\dfrac23v+\\dfrac{4}{15}+\\dfrac13v$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $v$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}{\\green{-\\dfrac{6}{5}}\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}v+\\green{\\dfrac{4}{15}}+\\blue{\\dfrac13}v}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}+\\blue{\\dfrac13}\\right)\\cdot v-\\green{\\dfrac{6}{5}}+\\green{\\dfrac{4}{15}}$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left(-\\dfrac13\\right)\\cdot v-\\dfrac{18}{15}+\\dfrac{4}{15}$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n$=-\\dfrac13v-\\dfrac{14}{15}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-\\frac{1}{3}v-\\frac{14}{15}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-\\frac{1}{3}v-\\frac{14}{15}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "b0a956b02f2b5aafbd190a8b3463b8c4", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  $-\\dfrac23p+\\dfrac15-1+\\dfrac56p$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $p$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}p+\\green{\\dfrac{1}{5}}\\green{-1}+\\blue{\\dfrac56}p}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac{2}{3}}+\\blue{\\dfrac56}\\right)\\cdot p+\\green{\\dfrac{1}{5}}-\\green{1}$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left({-\\dfrac{4}{6}}+{\\dfrac{5}{6}}\\right)\\cdot p+\\dfrac{1}{5}-\\dfrac{5}{5}$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{1}{6}}\\right)\\cdot p-\\dfrac{4}{5}$\n\n$=\\dfrac16p-\\dfrac{4}{5}$", "The simplified expression is $\\dfrac16p-\\dfrac45$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["\\frac{1}{6}p-\\frac{4}{5}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "\\frac{1}{6}p-\\frac{4}{5}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "8537b7ca50bb5fb2804b8a93c50dff40", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n$\\dfrac{11}{12}-\\dfrac16q+\\dfrac56q-\\dfrac13$  \n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $q$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}{\\green{\\dfrac{11}{12}}\\blue{-\\dfrac{1}{6}}q+\\blue{\\dfrac56}q\\green{-\\dfrac13}}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-\\dfrac{1}{6}}+\\blue{\\dfrac56}\\right)\\cdot q+\\green{\\dfrac{11}{12}}-\\green{\\dfrac13}$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left(\\dfrac46\\right)\\cdot q+\\dfrac{11}{12}-\\dfrac{4}{12}$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n$=\\left({\\dfrac{2}{3}}\\right)\\cdot q+\\dfrac{7}{12}$ [[☃ explanation 3]]\n\n$=\\dfrac23q+\\dfrac{7}{12}$", "The simplified expression is $\\dfrac23q+\\dfrac{7}{12}$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["\\frac{2}{3}q+\\frac{7}{12}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "\\frac{2}{3}q+\\frac{7}{12}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "5ff25039d60555f791ec0cbfb0b3426c", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to simplify the expression: **\n\n  ${1.17-0.07a+(-3.92a)}$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $a$ terms.\n\n", "$\\phantom{=}{1.17\\blue{-0.07}a+(\\blue{-3.92}a)}$\n\n$=1.17+\\left(\\blue{-0.07}+\\left(\\blue{-3.92}\\right)\\right)\\cdot a$\n\n$=1.17+\\left({-3.99}\\right)\\cdot a$\n\n$=1.17-3.99a$", "The simplified expression is $1.17-3.99a$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-3.99a+1.17"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-3.99a+1.17"}]}}}, {"item_id": "7912f7471c0658d1998ed3be26733984", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $1.3b+7.8-3.2b$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $b$ terms.\n\n", "$\\phantom{=}{\\blue{1.3}b+7.8\\blue{-3.2}b}$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{1.3}-\\blue{3.2}\\right)\\cdot b+7.8$\n\n$=\\left({-1.9}\\right)\\cdot b+7.8$\n\n$=-1.9b+7.8$", "The simplified expression is $-1.9b+7.8$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-1.9b+7.8"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-1.9b+7.8"}]}}}, {"item_id": "4a61839a238f552c9314992287192a5b", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to simplify the expression: **\n\n  $-5.55-8.55c+4.35c$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\text{\\blue{coefficients}}$ of the $c$ terms.\n\n", "$\\phantom{=}{-5.55\\blue{-8.55}c+\\blue{4.35}c}$\n\n$=-5.55+\\left(\\blue{-8.55}+\\blue{4.35}\\right)\\cdot c$\n\n$=-5.55+\\left({-4.2}\\right)\\cdot c$\n\n$=-5.55-4.2c$", "The simplified expression is $-5.55-4.2c$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-4.2c-5.55"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-4.2c-5.55"}]}}}, {"item_id": "5e92959d4d995f668bc0cd3d372798bc", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $3.26d+9.75d-2.65$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $d$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}\\blue{3.26}d+\\blue{9.75}d-2.65$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{3.26}+\\blue{9.75}\\right)\\cdot d-2.65$\n\n$=\\left(13.01\\right)\\cdot d-2.65$\n\n$=13.01d-2.65$", "The simplified expression is $13.01d-2.65$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["13.01d-2.65"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": "0", "simplify": false, "value": "13.01d-2.65"}]}}}, {"item_id": "6f54558d0fab5911a940fbc35ea8508b", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $0.25k+1.5-k-3.5$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $k$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}\\blue{0.25}k+\\green{1.5}\\blue{-1}k\\green{-3.5}$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{0.25}-\\blue{1}\\right)\\cdot k+\\green{1.5-3.5}$\n\n$=(-0.75)\\cdot k-2$\n\n$=-0.75k-2$", "The simplified expression is $-0.75k-2$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-0.75k-2"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-0.75k-2"}]}}}, {"item_id": "078e4ddcfa545e3490b324e63c3ef4ea", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $-3.6-1.9t+1.2+5.1t$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $t$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}\\green{-3.6}\\blue{-1.9}t+\\green{1.2}+\\blue{5.1}t$\n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-1.9}+\\blue{5.1}\\right)\\cdot t-\\green{3.6}+\\green{1.2}$\n\n$=(3.2)\\cdot t-2.4$\n\n$=3.2t-2.4$", "The simplified expression is $3.2t-2.4$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3.2t-2.4"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "3.2t-2.4"}]}}}, {"item_id": "e17eb8f1f1ec53e9bb929a46b751230f", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $-5.8c+4.2-3.1+1.4c$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $c$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$\\phantom{=}\\blue{-5.8}c+\\green{4.2}\\green{-3.1}+\\blue{1.4}c$ \n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-5.8}+\\blue{1.4}\\right)\\cdot c+\\green{4.2}-\\green{3.1}$\n\n$=(-4.4)\\cdot c+1.1$\n\n$=-4.4c+1.1$", "The simplified expression is $-4.4c+1.1$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-4.4c+1.1"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "-4.4c+1.1"}]}}}, {"item_id": "2001d461a91b5e54a31d85860f2a08d2", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $3.4-2.8d+2.8d-1.3$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Combine the $\\blue{\\text{coefficients}}$ of the $d$ terms, and combine the $\\green{\\text{constant}}$ terms.", "$3.4-2.8d+2.8d-1.3$\n\n$\\phantom{=}\\green{3.4}\\blue{-2.8}d+\\blue{2.8}d-\\green{1.3}$ \n\n$=\\left(\\blue{-2.8}+\\blue{2.8}\\right)\\cdot d+\\green{3.4}-\\green{1.3}$\n\n$=0\\cdot d+2.1$\n\n$=0+2.1$\n\n$=2.1$", "The simplified expression is 2.1."], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["2.1"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "form": false, "key": 0, "simplify": true, "value": "2.1"}]}}}, {"item_id": "b3b03bc4799055bd901d04f8a54d7a3c", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  $6\\left(\\dfrac{1}{2}w-\\dfrac{3}{4}\\right)$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Use the distributive property to multiply the $6$ into the parentheses.", "$\\phantom{=}\\pink6\\left(\\dfrac{1}{2}w-\\dfrac{3}{4}\\right)$\n\n$=\\pink6\\cdot \\dfrac12w-\\pink6\\cdot \\dfrac34$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=3w-\\dfrac{18}{4}$\n\n$=3w-\\dfrac92$ [[☃ explanation 2]]\n\n", "The expanded expression is $3w-\\dfrac92$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["3w-\\frac{9}{2}", "3w-\\frac{18}{4}"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": "0", "simplify": true, "value": "3w-\\frac{9}{2}"}, {"considered": "correct", "form": true, "key": 1, "simplify": false, "value": "3w-\\frac{18}{4}"}]}}}, {"item_id": "06cb83104e0c58e38db3122642fcb7e0", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter c