e terms to create an equivalent expression. **  \n*Enter any coefficients as simplified proper or improper fractions or integers.*\n\n  $\\dfrac17-3\\left(\\dfrac{3}{7}n-\\dfrac{2}{7}\\right)$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Use the distributive property to multiply the $\\pink{-3}$ into the parentheses.", "$\\phantom=\\dfrac17\\pink{-3}\\left(\\dfrac{3}{7}n-\\dfrac{2}{7}\\right)$\n\n$=\\dfrac17+(\\pink{-3})\\cdot\\left(\\dfrac37n\\right)+(\\pink{-3})\\cdot\\left(-\\dfrac27\\right)$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=\\dfrac17-\\dfrac97n+\\dfrac67$", "$=\\green{\\dfrac17}-\\dfrac97n+\\green{\\dfrac67}$\n\n$=-\\dfrac97n+\\dfrac77$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=-\\dfrac97n+1$", "The expanded expression is $-\\dfrac97n+1$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-\\frac{9}{7}n+1"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": "0", "simplify": true, "value": "-\\frac{9}{7}n+1"}]}}}, {"item_id": "71096ba87f1d52a8be9b571c8e7d2998", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $20\\left(-1.5r+0.75\\right)$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Use the distributive property to multiply the $20$ into the parentheses.", "$\\phantom{=}\\pink{20}\\left(-1.5r+0.75\\right)$\n\n$=\\pink{20}\\cdot\\left(-1.5r\\right)+\\pink{20}\\cdot 0.75$ [[☃ explanation 1]]\n\n$=-30r+15$", "The expanded expression is $-30r+15$"], "widget_types": ["expression"], "answer_data": {"expression 1": {"type": "expression", "correct_values": ["-30r+15"], "answerForms": [{"considered": "correct", "key": "0", "simplify": true, "value": "-30r+15"}]}}}, {"item_id": "1d9d5cf074ff55fbaa8bb70fc049815d", "question_content": "** Combine like terms to create an equivalent expression. **\n\n  $-2.5\\left(4x-3\\right)$\n\n[[☃ expression 1]]", "hints": ["Use the distributive property to multiply the $-2.5$ into the parentheses.", "$\\phantom{=}\\pink{-2.5}\\left(4x-3\\right)$\n\n$=\\pink{-2.5}\\cdot\\left(4x\\right)+(\\